  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Aim 1: To determine the incidence of glaucoma in Ghana in subjects previously found to be
      non-glaucomatous in the Tema Eye Survey.

      Aim 2: To characterise the progression of glaucoma and the outcomes of subjects diagnosed
      with glaucoma in the Tema Eye Survey.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
